@NODE Wozu " What does MEMake?"

	MEMake is a Makeutility. It have an GUI and is a Commodity.
	You can make MEMake to a programming exchange, all needed programs
	can startet, and so on...


@ENDNODE

@NODE bedienung " Usage"

	I thing the program is easy to use, but...

	All programs are startet Asynchron, you can go on work.
	
	The Tools and Info-Window are also Asynchron opened and
	you can spring between the windows with the TAB-key.

	In Stinggadget with extra Filerequester (e.g. Makefile in the
	Mainwindow) you can press the Help-Key in the Stringgadget
	and the Filerequster will oen.

	- @{" Mainwindow    " LINK "Hauptfenster"}
	- @{" Toolswindow   " LINK "Toolsfenster"}
	- @{" Infowindow    " LINK "Infofenster"}
	- @{" Prefswindow   " LINK "Prefsfenster"}
	- @{" Newwindow     " LINK "Neufenster"}
