@NODE Tooltypes " Tooltypes"

	In the Icon of MEMake you can use the Tooltypes:
	- CX_POPUP,CX_PRIORITY, CX_POPKEY (standart for Commodity)
	- PREFS=:
	 when you use this Tooltype the Program will load at the
	 start this Prefsfile
	- Name=:
	 this Makefile will be loaded at start (the Makefile in the
	 Prefsfile will be ignored)
 
@ENDNODE

